your secret master key (see *note Master key::) to produce a public key
(see *note Public keys::) that uniquely identifies that hyperdrive.

 -- Command: hyperdrive-new
     Create a new hyperdrive from a seed string.

   When you create a new drive, your chosen seed is used as its petname
(see *note Petnames::) by default.


